{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 19,
    "name": "سُورَةُ مَرۡيَمَ",
    "englishName": "Maryam",
    "englishNameTranslation": "Mary",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 98,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 2251,
        "text": "卡弗，哈，雅，阿因，撒德。",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2252,
        "text": "这是叙述你的主对于他的仆人宰凯里雅的恩惠。",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2253,
        "text": "当时，他低声地呼吁他的主说：",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2254,
        "text": "我的主啊！我的骨骼已软弱了，我已白发苍苍了，我的主啊！我没有为祈祷你而失望。",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2255,
        "text": "我的确担心我死后堂兄弟们不能继承我的职位，我的妻子又是不会生育的，求你赏赐我一个儿子，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2256,
        "text": "来继承我，并继承叶尔孤白的部分后裔。我的主啊！求你使他成为可喜的。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2257,
        "text": "宰凯里雅啊！我必定以一个儿子向你报喜，他的名字是叶哈雅，我以前没有使任何人与他同名。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2258,
        "text": "他说：我的主啊！我的妻子是不会生育的，我也老态龙钟了，我怎么会有儿子呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2259,
        "text": "主说：事情就是这样。你的主说：这对于我是容易的。以前你不存在，而我创造了你。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2260,
        "text": "他说：我的主啊！求你为我预定一种迹象。他说：你的迹象是你无疾无病，但三日三夜你不能和人说话。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2261,
        "text": "他从圣所里走出来见他的族人，就暗示他们：你们应当朝夕赞颂真主。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 305,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2262,
        "text": "叶哈雅啊！你应当坚持经典。他在童年时代我已赏赐他智慧，",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2263,
        "text": "与从我发出的恩惠和纯洁。他是敬畏的，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2264,
        "text": "是孝敬你的，不是霸道的，不是忤逆的。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2265,
        "text": "他在出生日、死亡日、复活日都享受和平。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 264,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2266,
        "text": "你应当在这部经典里提及麦尔彦，当日她离开了家属而到东边一个地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2267,
        "text": "她用一个帷幕遮蔽著，不让人们看见她。我使我的精神到她面前，他就对她显现成一个身材匀称的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2268,
        "text": "她说：我的确求庇于至仁主，免遭你的侵犯，如果你是敬畏的。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2269,
        "text": "他说：我只是你的主的使者，我来给你一个纯洁的儿子。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2270,
        "text": "她说：任何人没有接触过我，我又不是失节的，我怎么会有儿子呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2271,
        "text": "他说：事实是像这样的，你的主说：这对于我是容易的。我要以他为世人的迹象，为从我发出的恩惠，这是已经判决的事情。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 122,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2272,
        "text": "她就怀了孕，于是她退避到一个僻远的地方。",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2273,
        "text": "阵痛迫使她来到一棵椰枣树旁，她说：啊！但愿我以前死了，而且已变成被人遗忘的东西。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2274,
        "text": "椰枣树下有声音喊叫她说：你不要忧愁，你的主已在你的下面造化了一条溪水。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2275,
        "text": "你向著你的方向摇撼椰枣树，就有新鲜的、成熟的椰枣纷纷落在你的面前。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 306,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2276,
        "text": "你吃吧，你喝吧，你愉快吧！如果你见人来，你可以说：'我确已向至仁主发愿斋戒，所以今天我绝不对任何人说话'。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2277,
        "text": "她抱著婴儿来见她的族人，他们说：麦尔彦啊！你确已做了一件奇事。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2278,
        "text": "哈伦的妹妹啊！你父亲不是缺德的，你母亲不是失节的。",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2279,
        "text": "她就指一指那个婴儿，他们说：我们怎能对摇篮里的婴儿说话呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2280,
        "text": "那婴儿说：我确是真主的仆人，他要把经典赏赐我，要使我做先知，",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2281,
        "text": "要使我无论在那里都是有福的，并且嘱咐我，只要活著就要谨守拜功，完纳天课，",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2282,
        "text": "（他使我）孝敬我的母亲，他没有使我做霸道的、薄命的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2283,
        "text": "我在出生日、死亡日、复活日，都享受和平。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2284,
        "text": "这是麦尔彦的儿子尔萨，这是你们所争论的真理之言。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2285,
        "text": "真主不会收养儿子--赞颂真主、超绝万物--当他判决一件事的时候，他只对那件事说：有'，它就有了。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2286,
        "text": "真主确是我的主，也确是你们的主，所以你们应当崇拜他。这是正路。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2287,
        "text": "但各派之间意见分歧。重大日来临的时候，悲哀归于不信道者。",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2288,
        "text": "他们来见我的那日，他们的耳真聪，他们的眼真明，但不义者，今天确在明显的迷误之中。",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 307,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2289,
        "text": "你应当警告他们悔恨之日，当日一切事情已被判决，而他们现在还在疏忽之中。他们不信正道。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2290,
        "text": "我必定继承大地和大地上所有的一切，他们将归于我。",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 265,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2291,
        "text": "你应当在这部经典里提及易卜拉欣，他原是一个虔诚的人，又是一个先知。",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2292,
        "text": "当时他对他父亲说：我的父亲啊！你为何崇拜那既不能听，又不能见，对于你又没有任何裨益的东西呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2293,
        "text": "我的父亲啊！没有降临你的知识，确已降临我了；你顺从我吧，我要指示你一条正路。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2294,
        "text": "我的父亲啊！你不要崇拜恶魔，恶魔确是违抗至仁主的。",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2295,
        "text": "我的父亲啊！我的确怕你遭受从至仁主发出的刑罚，而变成恶魔的朋友。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2296,
        "text": "他说：你厌恶我的主宰吗？易卜拉欣啊！如果你不停止，我誓必辱骂你。你应当远离我个长时期。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2297,
        "text": "他说：祝你平安！我将为你向我的主求饶，他对我确是仁慈的。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2298,
        "text": "我将退避你们，以及你们舍真主而祈祷的。我将祈祷我的主，我或许不为祈祷我的主而变为薄命的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2299,
        "text": "他既退避他们，以及他们舍真主而祈祷的，我就赏赐他易司哈格和叶尔孤白，我使他俩成为先知，",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2300,
        "text": "我把我的恩惠赏赐他们，我使他们亨有真实的、崇高的声望。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 266,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2301,
        "text": "你应当在这部经典里提及穆萨，他确是纯洁的，确是使者，确是先知。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 308,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2302,
        "text": "我从那座山的右边召唤他，我叫他到我这里来密谈。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2303,
        "text": "我为了慈爱而把他哥哥先知哈伦给他做助手。",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2304,
        "text": "你应当在这部经典里提及易司马仪，他确是重然诺的，他是使者，又是先知。",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2305,
        "text": "他以拜功和天课命令他的家属，他在他的主那里是可喜的。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2306,
        "text": "你应当在这部经典里提及易德立斯，他是一个老实人，又是一个先知，",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2307,
        "text": "我把他提高到一个崇高的地位。",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2308,
        "text": "真主曾加以恩宠的这些先知，属于阿丹的后裔，属于我使（他们）与努哈同舟共济者的（后裔），属于易卜拉欣和易司拉仪的后裔，属于我所引导而且选拔的人，对他们宣读至仁主的启示的时候，他们俯伏下去叩头和哭泣。（此处叩头！）※",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 123,
        "sajda": {
          "id": 5,
          "recommended": true,
          "obligatory": false
        }
      },
      {
        "number": 2309,
        "text": "在他们去世之后，有不肖的后裔继承他们，那些后裔废弃拜功，顺从嗜欲，他们将遇迷误的果报。",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2310,
        "text": "但悔罪而信道，且行善者除外，他们将入乐园，不受丝毫亏待。",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2311,
        "text": "那是常住的乐园，至仁主在幽玄中应许其众仆的，他的诺言确是要履行的。",
        "numberInSurah": 61,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2312,
        "text": "他们在那里面，听不到闲谈，只听到祝愿平安；他们在那里面，朝夕获得给养。",
        "numberInSurah": 62,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2313,
        "text": "就是我将使众仆中的敬畏者继承的乐园。",
        "numberInSurah": 63,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2314,
        "text": "我们唯奉你的主的命令而随时降临，在我们面前的，在我们后面的，以及在我们前后之间的（事情），他都知道。你的主是不忘记的。",
        "numberInSurah": 64,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 309,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2315,
        "text": "他是天地万物的主，你应当崇拜他，你应当耐心，你知道他有匹敌吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 65,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 267,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2316,
        "text": "人说：我死后必要复活吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 66,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2317,
        "text": "人忘记了吗？他以前不是实有的，而我创造了他。",
        "numberInSurah": 67,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2318,
        "text": "指你的主发誓，我必将他们和众恶魔集合起来。然后我必使他们去跪在火狱的周围。",
        "numberInSurah": 68,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2319,
        "text": "然后我必从每一宗派中提出对至仁主最悖逆的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 69,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2320,
        "text": "然后，我的确知道谁是最该受火刑的。",
        "numberInSurah": 70,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2321,
        "text": "你们中没有一个人不到火狱的，那是你的主决定要施行的。",
        "numberInSurah": 71,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2322,
        "text": "然后，我将拯救敬畏者，而让不义者跪在那里面。",
        "numberInSurah": 72,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2323,
        "text": "对他们宣读我的明显的迹象的时候，不信道者对信道者说：哪一派的地位更优越，会场更优美呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 73,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2324,
        "text": "在他们之前，我曾毁灭了许多世代，无论资产和外观，都比他们更优美。",
        "numberInSurah": 74,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2325,
        "text": "你说：在迷误中的人愿至仁主优容他们，直到他们得见他们曾被警告的：不是刑罚，就是复活时他们就知道谁的地位更恶劣，谁的军队更懦弱了。",
        "numberInSurah": 75,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2326,
        "text": "真主将为遵循正道者增加其引导。常存的善功，在你的主看来是报酬更好，结局更善的。",
        "numberInSurah": 76,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 310,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2327,
        "text": "你告诉我吧！有人不信我的迹象，却说：我必要获得财产和子嗣。",
        "numberInSurah": 77,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2328,
        "text": "他曾窥见幽玄呢？还是他曾与至仁主订约呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 78,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2329,
        "text": "不然，我将记录他所说的，我将为他加重刑罚，",
        "numberInSurah": 79,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2330,
        "text": "我将继承他所说的财产和子嗣。而他将单身来见我。",
        "numberInSurah": 80,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2331,
        "text": "他们舍真主而崇拜许多主宰，作为自己的权利。",
        "numberInSurah": 81,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2332,
        "text": "不然，那些主宰将否认他们的崇拜，而变成他们的仇敌。",
        "numberInSurah": 82,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 268,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2333,
        "text": "你还不知道吗？我把恶魔们放出去诱惑不信道者，",
        "numberInSurah": 83,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2334,
        "text": "所以你对他们不要急躁，我只数他们的寿数。",
        "numberInSurah": 84,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2335,
        "text": "那日，我要把敬畏者集合到至仁主的那里，享受恩荣。",
        "numberInSurah": 85,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2336,
        "text": "我要把犯罪者驱逐到火狱去，以沸水解渴。",
        "numberInSurah": 86,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2337,
        "text": "但与至仁主订约者除外，人们不得说情。",
        "numberInSurah": 87,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2338,
        "text": "他们说：至仁主收养儿子。",
        "numberInSurah": 88,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2339,
        "text": "你们确已犯了一件重大罪行。为了那件罪行，",
        "numberInSurah": 89,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2340,
        "text": "天几乎要破，地几乎要裂，山几乎要崩。",
        "numberInSurah": 90,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2341,
        "text": "这是因为他们妄称人为至仁主的儿子。",
        "numberInSurah": 91,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2342,
        "text": "至仁主不会收养儿子，",
        "numberInSurah": 92,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2343,
        "text": "凡在天地间的，将来没有一个不像奴仆一样归依至仁主的。",
        "numberInSurah": 93,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2344,
        "text": "他确已统计过他们，检点过他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 94,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2345,
        "text": "复活日他们都要单身来见他。",
        "numberInSurah": 95,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 311,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2346,
        "text": "信道而且行善者，至仁主必定要使他们相亲相爱。",
        "numberInSurah": 96,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 312,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2347,
        "text": "我以你的语言，使《古兰经》成为容易的，只为要你借它向敬畏者报喜，并警告强辩的民众。",
        "numberInSurah": 97,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 312,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 2348,
        "text": "在他们之前，我曾毁灭了许多世代，你能发现那些世代中的任何人，或听见他们所发的微声吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 98,
        "juz": 16,
        "manzil": 4,
        "page": 312,
        "ruku": 269,
        "hizbQuarter": 124,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
